      <para id="para-00005">This is consistent with the solution we found earlier, with a difference of one cent due to rounding error.</para>
      <para id="para-00006">We may also use the calculator to solve for the present value of a mixed cash stream. Earlier in this chapter, we asked how much money you would need today to fund the following five annual withdrawals, with each withdrawal made at the end of the year, beginning one year from now, and all remaining money earning 6% compounded annually:</para>
