      <para id="para-00022">Again, Rate is the interest rate; Value1, Value 2, and so on are the cash flows; and “Formula result” is the answer.</para>
      <para id="para-00023">Let us apply the NPV function to our problem, as shown in <link target-id="fig-00005" document="m00059"/> and <link target-id="fig-00006" document="m00059"/>.</para>
